name: AnimeChar - Oshi Mix | Arima Kana (有馬 かな | 有馬 佳奈)
description:
Greetings to all,

We are pleased to announce the launch of our new series, Oshi Mix, which is part of AnimeChar. Our aim is to generate a specific character using Lora based on our extensive dataset.

In this series, we would like to introduce our newly trained Lora model of Arima Kana (有馬 かな), a child prodigy and actress, a friend of Aquamarine and Ruby Hoshino, and the centre of the renewed B-Komachi.

You can support our work by buying us a drink through the following link: https://www.buymeacoffee.com/ryalandai.
You can also follow our Instagram account for AI painting and model updates: https://www.instagram.com/rya.land.ai.
If you like our model, we would appreciate it if you could give us a 5-star rating.


For more information about the model version and the characters it includes, please take a look at the 'About this version' section. The model we used as a foundation is called Anything v4.0, and we have included sample images created by at least two different base models.

-- Please also support --

AnimeChar - Railgun Mix

Misaka Mikoto (御坂 美琴) || Shirai Kuroko (白井 黑子)

AnimeChar - Oshi Mix

Kurokawa Akane (黒川 あかね) || Kotōbuki Minami (寿 みなみ)

Arima Kana (有馬 かな) || Hoshino Rubi (星野瑠美衣) [v2.0] || Hoshino Ai (星野 アイ)

AnimeChar - Hyouka Mix

Chitanda Eru (千反田 える)
AnimeChar - Liz Bird Mix
Kasaki Nozomi (傘木 希美)

AnimeChar - Tamako Mix

Kitashirakawa Tamako (北白川 たまこ) & Asagiri Shiori (朝霧 史織)

AnimeFus - KyoMix

Nichijou (日常) Special || v0.3
